{"body": "I think what @pixeltrix meant was that you don't need to require the text_helper explicitly since it'll auto-load when you require action_view:\r\n\r\n    1.9.2p290 :001 > require 'action_view'\r\n     => true \r\n    1.9.2p290 :002 > class Foo; include ActionView::Helpers::TextHelper; end\r\n     => Foo \r\n    1.9.2p290 :003 > Foo.new.strip_tags('<a href=\"#bar\">ohai</a>')\r\n     => \"ohai\"", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3113177", "created_at": "2011-12-12T21:33:53Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3943#issuecomment-3113177", "updated_at": "2011-12-12T21:33:53Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3943, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/spagalloco", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6cb846fa3915943695482f6bf78084b7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F79aadfd37377569522c12e25d973b68e.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6cb846fa3915943695482f6bf78084b7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "spagalloco", "type": "User", "id": 28044, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52382f67bd3543c15100f54a"}, "id": 3113177, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3943"}
